<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="378" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="6.[98,1306,1120,2961]" pageId="6" pageNumber="378">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[101,459,2773,2802]" pageId="6" pageNumber="378">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
CITES Appendix III. Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List (as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="F. Cuvier" authorityYear="1825" box="[345,602,2809,2842]" class="Mammalia" family="Erethizontidae" genus="Sphiggurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="6" pageNumber="378" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Sphiggurus spinosus</taxonomicName>
and S. villosus). Less than 20% ofthe likely habitat of the Paraguayan Hairy Dwarf Porcupine in Brazil is protected.
</paragraph>
